📝 AI Resume Analyzer
An AI-powered Resume Analyzer built using Flask, spaCy, and PyPDF2. This web application extracts key details from resumes, matches skills with job requirements, and provides feedback based on a calculated score.

🚀 Features
✅ Extracts Name, Email, Phone Number, Skills, Awards, and Projects
✅ Uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) for entity extraction
✅ Matches resume skills with required job roles
✅ Analyzes experience and calculates a resume score
✅ Provides personalized feedback to improve resumes

📌 Tech Stack
Python
Flask (Web Framework)
spaCy (NLP)
PyPDF2 (PDF Text Extraction)
HTML/CSS (Frontend)
